column5: Well good morning all, hope everyone has a great day.  It's a bit stormy up here right now...lots of noise anyway, has been through the night.  It's just starting to rain now, and me with only one working wiper   .  Goes to show the weather newtork doesn't know much, they say this is supposed to come this afternoon....oh well, good for the lawn right  Have a great day all, and stay cool.  Maureen
Morning chilluns. Well, this morning I woke up so that's a good start right there. Have a great day Maureen et al.
G'day all, gonna be another fine day fer sure !!
Good Mornin' y'all!!! Hope everyone has a great day!  Wishin' I was fishin' instead of workin' like a dog!
Good Morning! This working for a living has gotten old.   Whopper
Good morning everyone.... I'm already at yard...... watched the lightning show north of us on the drive in.... sure is pretty... lol  Have a great day everyone
Jeez, I got to sleep in today until 7:10, usually it's about 6 or so when my little girls wake up daddy. You guys are up wayyyy to early!!!
